{"title":"proxy_pool搭建过程","slug":"proxy-pool搭建过程","date":"2021-12-25T13:24:05.000Z","updated":"2021-12-25T14:05:24.736Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/proxy-pool搭建过程.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://wansuw.gitee.iohttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wanswu/images/image-20211225212641539.webp"],"content":"<p>一、使用docker搭建一个redis</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight dockerfile\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull redis</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"keyword\">run</span><span class=\"bash\"> -p 6379:6379 --name myredis -v D:/Docker/redis/:/etc/redis/ -d redis redis-server /etc/redis/redis.conf --appendonly no</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>二、配置proxy_pool中的setting</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wanswu/images/image-20211225212641539.webp\"></p>\n<p>三、拉取proxy_pool</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight dockerfile\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull jhao104/proxy_pool</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"keyword\">run</span><span class=\"bash\"> --env DB_CONN=redis://:password@ip:port/0 -p 5010:5010 jhao104/proxy_pool:2.4.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","more":"<p>一、使用docker搭建一个redis</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight dockerfile\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull redis</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"keyword\">run</span><span class=\"bash\"> -p 6379:6379 --name myredis -v D:/Docker/redis/:/etc/redis/ -d redis redis-server /etc/redis/redis.conf --appendonly no</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>二、配置proxy_pool中的setting</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wanswu/images/image-20211225212641539.webp\"></p>\n<p>三、拉取proxy_pool</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight dockerfile\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull jhao104/proxy_pool</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"keyword\">run</span><span class=\"bash\"> --env DB_CONN=redis://:password@ip:port/0 -p 5010:5010 jhao104/proxy_pool:2.4.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}